<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.11">
<l>kūṭivaṇ ṭaṟaiyun taṇtārk koṇṭalpōl vaṇṇaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>māṭalar poḻilku rukūr vaṇcaṭa kōpaṉ coṉṉa</l>
<l>pāṭalō rāyirattu ḷivaiyumoru pattum vallār</l>
<l>vīṭila pōka meyti virumpuva ramarar moyttē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master this one decade in the one thousand songs</l>
<l>spoken by liberal Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr with rich-blooming groves</l>
<l>on the one with a colour like the clouds with a cool garland where bees join [and] hum</l>
<l>reaching enjoyment without loss the immortals will swarm around [and] desire [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
